OL,3,C50 Years On: The Death Sentence, the
OL,4,CDictator, and the Cardiff Pool
OL,6,FIt's 50 years since one of the more
OL,7,Fsurreal moments in British diplomatic
OL,8,Fhistory: a tense international
OL,9,Fstandoff that brought together a
OL,10,FBritish lecturer, an infamous
OL,11,Fdictator, and a swimming pool in
OL,12,FCardiff.
OL,14,FIt was July 1975.JBack then, Uganda
OL,15,Fwas ruled by one of the most feared
OL,16,Ftyrants of the 20th century: Idi Amin.
