OL,3,C50 Years On: The Death Sentence, the
OL,4,CDictator, and the Cardiff Pool
OL,6,FA former British colonial soldier,
OL,7,FAmin had seized power in a military
OL,8,Fcoup and declared himself president.
OL,9,FHis rule quickly descended into
OL,10,Fbrutality. Known for his erratic
OL,11,Fbehaviour and self styling as the
OL,12,F"Last King of Scotland," Amin turned
OL,13,FUganda into a police state marked by
OL,14,Fmass killings, disappearances, and
OL,15,Fpersecution.
