OL,3,C50 Years On: The Death Sentence, the
OL,4,CDictator, and the Cardiff Pool
OL,6,FWhat happened next - nobody could be
OL,7,Fsure.
OL,9,FInto the room came the huge figure of
OL,10,FIdi Amin, there to meet him, the man
OL,11,Fdubbed as 'farmer Jim'.
OL,13,FAmin walked up to the Foreign
OL,14,FSecretary and immediately gave him a
OL,15,Fbear hug. His first words?
OL,17,F"When I knew you came from Cardiff, I
OL,18,Fdecided I was going to release Hills
OL,19,Fto you."
