OL,3,C50 Years On: The Death Sentence, the
OL,4,CDictator, and the Cardiff Pool
OL,6,FA transcript of that meeting,
OL,7,Frediscovered 50 years on, reveals the
OL,8,Fdictator's peculiar fondness for
OL,9,FWales. Amin reminisces about visiting
OL,10,FCardiff during his time as a soldier
OL,11,Fin the British Army.
OL,13,FAmin: "You come from Wales?"
OL,15,FCallaghan: "Yes"
OL,17,FAmin: "I like it very much, very
OL,18,Fgreen. When I was in England, I spent
OL,19,Fmy weekends there.."
OL,21,FCallaghan: "Did you really?"
