OL,6,FAmin: "Yes, I like it very much.
OL,7,FCardiff I've been there."
OL,9,FCallaghan: "Very glad to hear it"
OL,11,FAmin: "You have a swimming pool there"
OL,13,FCallaghan: "Did you ever try it?"
OL,15,FAmin: "I swam there in 1964, August."
