OL,6,FWith that Hills and Callaghan would
OL,7,Fleave for the UK.JThe three men would
OL,8,Fhave very different fates.
OL,10,FJim Callaghan would go on to become
OL,11,FPrime Minister.
OL,13,FIdi Amin was overthrown in 1979 and
OL,14,Ffled into exile. He died in Saudi
OL,15,FArabia in 2003 - unrepentant of his
OL,16,Frule in Uganda.
