OL,3,C50 Years On: The Death Sentence, the
OL,4,CDictator, and the Cardiff Pool
OL,6,FAs for Denis Hills, he returned to
OL,7,FBritain a reluctant celebrity. He
OL,8,Fcontinued to write and lecture, though
OL,9,Fhe largely retreated from the
OL,10,Fspotlight. He died in 2004, aged 90.
OL,12,FHis story, and the bizarre twist of
OL,13,Fhistory that tied Uganda to Wales,
OL,14,Fremains one of the strangest episodes
OL,15,Fin British diplomacy. A moment where a
OL,16,Fswimming pool in Cardiff may have
OL,17,Fhelped save a man's life, all because
OL,18,Fa dictator used to swim there.
